Docs.summary: Gets the number of messages that will be eagerly requested from Queues or Subscriptions during processing. This is intended to help maximize throughput by allowing the processor to receive from a local cache rather than waiting on a service request.
Docs.value: The prefetch count is specified using and has a default value of 0.
